flowchart LR
  DEV[Developer Branch] --> PR[Pull Request]
  PR --> LINT[Lint / Format]
  LINT --> TEST[Unit + Contract Tests]
  TEST --> SEC[SAST / SCA]
  SEC --> BUILD[Build OCI Images]
  BUILD --> SCAN[Image Scan + SBOM]
  SCAN --> REG[Push Registry]
  REG --> DEVENV[Deploy Dev]
  DEVENV --> INT[Integration Tests]
  INT --> STAGE[Deploy Staging]
  STAGE --> E2E[E2E + Security Gates]
  E2E --> APPROVE[Release Approval]
  APPROVE --> PROD[Prod Canary / Blue-Green]
